Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微外出一下去取材吧
